Killing Wind grants the following for 5 seconds, and is refreshed to 5 seconds after each kill to a max of 8 seconds: +20 Range, 50 Mobility, 40 Handling, +30% reduced ADS movement penalty, +5% increased damage falloff.

Repulsor Brace grants 45HP Overshield on Void-debuffed kill.

Range on Master.
Armor Piercing boosts damage by 5%, Range +5, and penetrates the target shield.
Swarm of the Raven increases the damage by 50% when an allied player uses the exotic Tractor Cannon against a boss.

Subsistence allows you to spam more shots. Your gun will auto-reload five bullets back into the magazine, which is the amount of ammo the Wyvern shot takes.

Onslaught, on the other hand, boosts the ADS variant of the gun, allowing it to mow through trash mobs a little quicker.
